trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of DataColumnMapping objects, and is implemented by the <see cref="T:System.Data.Common.DataColumnMappingCollection" />, which is used in common by .NET Framework data providers.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção de objetos DataColumnMapping e é implementado pelo <see cref="T:System.Data.Common.DataColumnMappingCollection" />, que é usado em comum por provedores de dados .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> interface enables an inheriting class to implement a ColumnMapping collection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> interface permite que uma classe implementar uma coleção de ColumnMapping de herança.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [DataAdapter DataTable and DataColumn Mappings](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/dataadapter-datatable-and-datacolumn-mappings.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [DataAdapter DataTable e DataColumn mapeamentos](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/dataadapter-datatable-and-datacolumn-mappings.md).

trans-unit.source: An application does not create an instance of the <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> interface directly, but creates an instance of a class that inherits <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Um aplicativo não cria uma instância do <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> interface diretamente, mas cria uma instância de uma classe que herda <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection>.

trans-unit.source: Classes that inherit <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> must implement all inherited members, and typically define additional members to add provider-specific functionality.
trans-unit.target: As classes que herdam <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> deve implementar membros herdados todas as e geralmente definem membros adicionais para adicionar funcionalidade específica do provedor.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> interface defines the <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection.RemoveAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection> interface define o <xref:System.Data.IColumnMappingCollection.RemoveAt%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: In turn, the <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMappingCollection> class inherits this method, and defines two additional overloads of <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMappingCollection.RemoveAt%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Por sua vez, o <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMappingCollection> classe herda esse método e define duas sobrecargas adicionais do <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMappingCollection.RemoveAt%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The following example uses an instance of the derived class, <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMapping>, to <xref:System.Data.Common.DataColumnMappingCollection.Add%2A> several <xref:System.Data.Common.DataColumnMapping> objects to its <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMapping.ColumnMappings%2A> collection, and then displays a list of those mapped source tables.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir usa uma instância da classe derivada, <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMapping>, <xref:System.Data.Common.DataColumnMappingCollection.Add%2A> vários <xref:System.Data.Common.DataColumnMapping> objetos em seu <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMapping.ColumnMappings%2A> tabelas de origem de coleção e, em seguida, exibe uma lista dessas mapeado.

trans-unit.source: This example assumes that a <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMapping> has already been created.
trans-unit.target: Este exemplo supõe que um <xref:System.Data.Common.DataTableMapping> já foi criado.
